biography: Jari is a rising star from Archipelagia Golf Club, making his mark on the competitive golf scene.  He brings a powerful and precise game to the course, and his presence in the Hector Trophée is always one to watch.

This will be Jari’s second appearance at the prestigious Hector Trophée, his first being in 2025. While he hasn't yet claimed victory in the main competition or earned the Victor trophy for individual excellence, his steady improvement and impressive skill set suggest that this year could be different. Jari is a player to keep an eye on as he navigates the challenges of this year's tournament.
